name: Air Canada Orders the A321neo!
description:
On March 22nd, 2022, Air Canada announced their biggest new aircraft order since the CSeries - for 26 Airbus A321neos!

The first of these planes, which are XLR versions, will start being delivered in the first quarter of 2024, with deliveries continuing until 2027.

Let's take a look at what this might mean for the airline!
